      "groupIds": [
        "type_5"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: \"5/3 times FASTER\" = Sa = (1+5/3)Sb\n  = (8/3)Sb (NOT same as 5/3 times as fast!)\nStep 2: D/(8/3 Sb) = (D-80)/Sb\n  3D/8 = D-80 → 3D = 8D-640\n  5D = 640 → D = 128m\n\n  \"AS FAST\":  Sa = k x Sb      (5/3 x Sb)\n  \"FASTER\":   Sa = (1+k) x Sb  (8/3 x Sb)\n              ^^^ TRAP: different meanings!\n\nTRICK:\nAlways check which interpretation fits!\nD/(D-80) = 8/3 → D=128\n\nAnswer: Winning post at 128 metres ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
