    {
      "id": "el_45",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1271,
      "width": 324,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=1000 → B=950. When B=1000 → C=960\nStep 2: Scale: when B=950, C=960×950/1000\n  C = 912m\nStep 3: A beats C by 1000-912 = 88m\n\n  Start                        Finish(1000m)\n  |================================| A\n  |=============================   | B (950m)\n  |==========================      | C (912m)\n  A beats C = 1000-912 = 88m\n\nTRICK (formula):\nA beats C = X+Y-XY/D = 50+40-2000/1000 = 88m\n\nAnswer: A beats C by 88 metres ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
