      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=1000 → B=950. When B=1000 → C=960\nStep 2: Scale: when B=950, C=960×950/1000\n  C = 912m\nStep 3: A beats C by 1000-912 = 88m\n\n  Start                        Finish(1000m)\n  |================================| A\n  |=============================   | B (950m)\n  |==========================      | C (912m)\n  A beats C = 1000-912 = 88m\n\nTRICK (formula):\nA beats C = X+Y-XY/D = 50+40-2000/1000 = 88m\n\nAnswer: A beats C by 88 metres ✓",
