      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1617,
      "width": 830,
      "height": 49,
      "text": "A runs at 10 m/s and B runs at 8 m/s. In a 100 meter race,\nhow much of a head start should A give B so that they\nfinish at the same time?",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
