    {
      "id": "el_55",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1698,
      "width": 281,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: When A=100: B=90, C=80\nStep 2: Sb:Sc = 90:80 = 9:8\nStep 3: When B=100, C = 100×8/9 = 88.89\n  B beats C by 100-88.89 = 11.11m\n\n  When A=100: B=90, C=80\n  Scale to B=100: C = 80x100/90 = 88.89\n  TRAP: 20-10 = 10? NO! Answer = 11.11m\n\nTRICK:\nB beats C = D × (1 - Sc/Sb)\n= 100 × (1 - 80/90) = 100/9 = 11.11m\n\nAnswer: B beats C by 11.11 metres ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
