    {
      "id": "el_60",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1698,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: When A=100: B=80, C=72\n  Sb/Sa = 0.8, Sc/Sa = 0.72\nStep 2: Sc/Sb = 0.72/0.8 = 0.9\nStep 3: When B=100, C = 100×0.9 = 90\n  B gives C = 100-90 = 10 pts\n\n  A=100 pts: B=80, C=72 (given)\n  Scale B->100: C = 72x100/80 = 90\n  B gives C = 100-90 = 10 pts\n\nTRICK:\nGames = Races (pts = distance)\nC when B finishes = 100 × Sc/Sb\n\nAnswer: B can give C 10 points ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
