        "type_9"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: When A=100: B=80, C=72\n  Sb/Sa = 0.8, Sc/Sa = 0.72\nStep 2: Sc/Sb = 0.72/0.8 = 0.9\nStep 3: When B=100, C = 100×0.9 = 90\n  B gives C = 100-90 = 10 pts\n\n  A=100 pts: B=80, C=72 (given)\n  Scale B->100: C = 72x100/80 = 90\n  B gives C = 100-90 = 10 pts\n\nTRICK:\nGames = Races (pts = distance)\nC when B finishes = 100 × Sc/Sb\n\nAnswer: B can give C 10 points ✓",
