    },
    {
      "id": "el_65",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 2095,
      "width": 274,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A's time = 200/10 = 20s\nStep 2: B's time = 20+4 = 24s\nStep 3: B's speed = 200/24 = 25/3 m/s\n\n  A: |===200m===| 20s   (Sa=10)\n  B: |===200m=======| 24s  (Sb=?)\n     Ta + 4s = Tb → Sb = 200/24 = 8.33\n\nTRICK:\nTb = Ta + T_beaten = 20+4 = 24s\nSb = D/Tb = 200/24 = 8.33 m/s\n\nAnswer: B's speed = 8.33 m/s ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 6500,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 65,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_10"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A's time = 200/10 = 20s\nStep 2: B's time = 20+4 = 24s\nStep 3: B's speed = 200/24 = 25/3 m/s\n\n  A: |===200m===| 20s   (Sa=10)\n  B: |===200m=======| 24s  (Sb=?)\n     Ta + 4s = Tb → Sb = 200/24 = 8.33\n\nTRICK:\nTb = Ta + T_beaten = 20+4 = 24s\nSb = D/Tb = 200/24 = 8.33 m/s\n\nAnswer: B's speed = 8.33 m/s ✓",
